high_descs: turn around and head to the sink
take out a lettuce from the sink
turn around and head to the fridge
place the lettuce to cool in the fridge and take it out
turn left and head to the sink
place the lettuce by the side of the sink
anns.task_desc: place a cold lettuce by the side of the sink

high_descs: Turn around, move to the sink.
Pick up the lettuce in the sink.
Turn around, bring the lettuce to the fridge on the left.
Chill the lettuce in the fridge.
Bring the chilled lettuce back to the sink.
Put the lettuce on the counter right of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put chilled lettuce on the counter.

high_descs: Walk over to the kitchen sink.
Pick up the head of lettuce that is in the kitchen sink.
Turn around and walk forward, then hang a left and walk up to the fridge.
Open the fridge and put the head of lettuce inside then close the door, after a couple seconds open the fridge and take out the head of lettuce then close the door.
Turn left and walk over to the kitchen sink.
Put the chilled head of lettuce on the counter to the right of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled head of lettuce on the counter.
